T1  - Benefits beyond the local network: Does indirect international collaboration ties contribute to research performance for young scientists?
AU  - Chen, Kaihua
AU  - Ding, Yi
AU  - Zhao, Binbin
AU  - Guo, Rui
AU  - Ning, Lutao
JO  - Research Policy
