T1  - The effect of trainee career intentions on mentor's interest in the trainee: Experimental evidence from academia
AU  - Smirnova, Inna
AU  - Shannon, Austin
AU  - Teplitskiy, Misha
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 54
IS  - 5
SP  - 105232
