T1  - When citizens judge science: Crowd evaluations in Mode 2 knowledge production
AU  - Franzoni, Chiara
AU  - Sauermann, Henry
AU  - Di Marco, Diletta
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 54
IS  - 5
SP  - 105214
PY  - 2025
