T1  - Looking under the hood—How incumbent characteristics reduce the innovation impact of trajectory-changing demand-pull policy mixes for battery electric vehicles
AU  - Luetkehaus, Hauke
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 54
IS  - 5
SP  - 105212
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/06/01/
SN  - 0048-7333
